name: Moneyland
description: A bustling financial district in a cyberpunk megalopolis. Procedurally generated using Voronoi textures and JSPlacement with added holograms, traffic, and weather effects. Rendered in Blender Eevee. Featured OBJKT: #4615 "rotterdam-architecture-vector" by Scott X (@spike_0124). By Lucius Felimus: https://www.luciusfelimus.com/
